# pico-386 cart integration manifest
#
# Format (TSV, '#' lines and blank lines ignored):
#   <dos_name>\t<url>\t<sha256-or-"-">\t<license>\t<source>
#
# - dos_name : 8.3 stem used on the FAT floppy (uppercased, no extension).
# - url      : direct download URL of a .p8.png cartridge.
# - sha256   : expected SHA-256 of the downloaded file, or '-' to skip verify.
# - license  : SPDX-ish identifier of the cart's license.
# - source   : human-readable origin (project / author / repo path).
#
# Only permissively-licensed carts go in this file. Proprietary Lexaloffle BBS
# carts must NOT be added here; supply them locally via the LEXALOFFLE_CARTS_DIR
# environment variable (see test/CARTS.md).
#
# When sha256 is '-', the runner downloads anyway but prints a warning. After
# verifying a cart works, lock its hash in by replacing '-' with the real sum
# (printed by `script/fetch_carts.sh --print-hashes`).
#
# ── picotool sample carts (MIT) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# https://github.com/dansanderson/picotool — sample/test carts shipped under
# the repository's MIT license. Raw URLs pin to a specific commit for
# reproducibility; bump the SHA when intentionally rolling forward.
PTOOLCRT	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dansanderson/picotool/49808e5ddb21e886a5608a19c95ec3ca6f1ee541/tests/testdata/test_cart.p8.png	4a0c90794114ae0f2aa46ab42c926fcf09d898b4bce3df1f6ed831ad18540798	MIT	picotool@49808e5d:tests/testdata/test_cart.p8.png

# ── shrinko8 sample carts (MIT) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# https://github.com/thisismypassport/shrinko8
# (Add specific entries here once a known-good commit + path is verified.)

# ── fake-08 sample carts (MIT) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# https://github.com/jtothebell/fake-08
# (Add specific entries here once a known-good commit + path is verified.)
CPARSE	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jtothebell/fake-08/814991a2571ad3970e386cef48f3b148aa1c27b9/test/carts/cartparsetest.p8.png	555ef0afed7a4b9e7826c65440b03f63f16cfb4624d6792363f70b4e130981b2	MIT	fake-08@814991a2:test/carts/cartparsetest.p8.png
